{"tid":961244,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"[認真] 覺唔覺得何WAYNE喺足球評論方面冇乜進步?","createTime":"2018-12-30T03:20:08.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-30T04:56:43.000Z","uid":84081,"like":0,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"c0d62f560fdc730f274effb5e070fc829f21ea7d","tid":961244,"uid":84081,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-30T03:20:08.000Z","msg":"首先我有時都幾BUY佢既理論 例如343係好難破密集<br />\n<br />\n但係佢製作評論片既質素真係冇進步過 有時見到啲垃圾求奇剪下周星馳戲入面5分鐘都可以呃到1百萬VIEW, 而何蛇某啲片得幾千VIEW, 真心鄧佢唔抵 <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/clown2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n認真如果想多啲VIEW同多啲人訂閱, 不如係某啲片花多啲心機製作, 甚至考慮請個幫手一齊製作<br />\n到時VIEW多咗就可以更有尊嚴地生活落去<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  我地VIEWER又睇得開心, 又易啲SHARE畀其他人一齊睇<br />\n<br />\n1) 賽後評試下加入圖去解釋&quot;半主角&quot; &quot;綠葉插入&quot; 等慨念 可以用返場波既平面圖黎解釋<br />\n如果用到場波既FOOTAGE當然最好 但可能有版權問題唔用得 我都明白 <br />\n平面圖畫公仔係冇版權既 詳細點做可以參考外國既足球YOUTUBER<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Nrt2HTm.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FNrt2HTm.png&h=c6de7d6a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/sbsODsG.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FsbsODsG.jpg&h=c65c6040&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/EQAD0F1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FEQAD0F1.jpg&h=05f3f914&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n最簡單你整個IPAD PRO再用PENCIL係上面畫 FASTFORWARD個動作 再加埋你另外錄音<br />\n件事已經好清晰 <br />\n<br />\n又或者多啲轉換畫面 貼下HEAT MAP 解釋下連加特點樣唔拉邊成日死係中路搞到冇乜進攻套路<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ZRcGd2i.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FZRcGd2i.jpg&h=7e8462be&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n2) 錄音質素唔好<br />\n啲P, F音噴曬落支MIC度搞到好多雜聲 整返個罩 長遠有BUDGET既時候買過支PRO MIC<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/v6OaRKT.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fv6OaRKT.png&h=7ef5212d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Zz8aRKT.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FZz8aRKT.png&h=ee8188f3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n暫時諗到咁多 希望何蛇會睇到呢個POST.<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1de2812debd4f3dae74cb222e7ce78f6f0a48381","tid":961244,"uid":12000,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-30T03:20:48.000Z","msg":"咖啡灌腸"},{"pid":"fd83f507f7cc0cc0da43f669c3f64a58700c2332","tid":961244,"uid":20224,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-30T03:22:24.000Z","msg":"唔係得fifa界面啫咩"},{"pid":"4d7ae46501ed39dd26e41385261969e95b3e35ab","tid":961244,"uid":47558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-30T03:25:42.000Z","msg":"我覺得佢重點評一兩場波，條片整靚 d 好過啦"},{"pid":"5dbd4cccf05f59eacd9ac5aeadd7e634e3f0cf2d","tid":961244,"uid":38962,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-30T03:29:12.000Z","msg":"其實佢日日都評咁多場波，咁佢係有講到每場波好多細節位<br />\n但就係睇得太密，完全無時間剪接片段，所以變左咁既問題"},{"pid":"90129bdff65d7f149065b75409de73ac44e0ec31","tid":961244,"uid":39269,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-30T04:56:43.000Z","msg":"淨係上次車贏鏝嗰場理性分析好佢10倍啦，真係分析哂企位走位問題，同教練成場取態變化"}]}